  <h2>📊 What’s a Healthy Body Fat Range?</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Men:</strong> 10–20% is typical, 6–13% for athletes</li>
    <li><strong>Women:</strong> 18–28% is typical, 14–20% for athletes</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>🔁 How Often Should You Measure?</h2>
  <p>Check every 2–4 weeks. Take measurements in the morning and under similar conditions to track true progress.</p>

